---
<section id="about" class="text-[var(--white)] py-12 md:py-24 border-t border-[#ffffff10]">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-lg text-[var(--sec)] mb-2 shiny-sec">About Me</h2>
    <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium mb-12">Engineering scalable AI solutions</h3>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="text-[var(--white-icon)] space-y-6 md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          I am an AI Automation Engineer and Full Stack Developer based in Karachi, Pakistan. I focus on turning complex business problems into clean, automated solutions that work in the real world — not just in demos.
        </p>
        <p>
          I specialize in building AI agents, LLM-powered pipelines, and full-stack web applications. Whether it is automating a repetitive workflow, integrating multiple SaaS tools, or deploying a customer-facing AI assistant, I bring both the technical depth and product thinking to get it done right.
        </p>
        <p>
          I work across the full stack — from FastAPI backends and vector databases to React frontends and CI/CD pipelines — so I can own a project end-to-end without any gaps.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center flex-col gap-4">
        <div class="w-full h-72 md:h-96 rounded-2xl bg-[#1414149c] border border-[var(--white-icon-tr)] flex items-center justify-center flex-col text-[var(--white-icon)] hover:border-[var(--white-icon)] transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_-5px_var(--sec)]">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mb-4 text-[var(--sec)]">
            <path d="M12 2v20"></path>
            <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path>
          </svg>
          <span class="font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-[var(--white)]">INNOVATION THROUGH CODE</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
